  "title": "HR Executive",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Recruitment and selection for support and assigned positions</li>\n  <li>Manage complete process of all foreign work passes (EP/SP/DP) applications, renewals and terminations.</li>\n  <li>Manage the payroll &amp; CPF &amp; insurance matters, including statutory submission (CPF, Government paid leave, Foreign tax clearance, etc.), as well as e-filing (IR8E).</li>\n  <li>Involvement and partnering in policy implementation</li>\n  <li>Oversee General Administrative Matters</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of payroll processes, regulations, and compliance requirements.</li>\n  <li>Good experience with work permit management- application, renewal, appeal, and cancellation</li>\n  <li>Able to multi-task under pressure</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 4 - 5 years' work experience in the field of HR</li>\n  <li>With experience in agency is a plus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
